nodes.bodyText: Why are these deleted all over the place? (i.e. please explain the connection between the code change and this change in the generated comments)

I changed the pattern of the field resource from Book to * to repro this issue: https://github.com/googleapis/gapic-generator/pull/3138/files#diff-4c8eaf76addf344f8abf6b2800029f9eR51
And the comment is no longer correct... so I deleted the comment, hence the change is baseline.
